1.Explain the use of JavaScript ( or What you can do using a JavaScript)
In today javascript is getting used as the frontend ,backend, middleware ,machine learning , AI, blockchain and more.

2.What is the difference between client-side and server-side?
Client-side simply means the core functionality is running on the client machine. like if i am operating website and interacting with browing moving from one page to another thats the client side.
Server-side means the core fuctionality is running on the server . like we know some pcs are never shut down or always online they are having their own cli and other programe which we are using as server.

3.What is Nodejs?
Nodejs creates is a open source programme which creates the enviroment to run javascript.

4.Explain Scope in JavaScript
Scope defines the use of the function,variable and objects.

